1. Install Java JDK 1.8 (latest version) and set the JAVA_HOME

2. Install the latest eclipse version

3. Import the existing project/ create new Java Project

4. Add following Dependencies in the Project:
testng-6.9.9.jar
Selenium 2.53 jars
Apache-poi (For Excel Connectivity)
Monte Repack (For Video Recording)
gson-2.3.1.jar (Already added in selenium jars)
guava-19.0.jar (Already added in selenium jars)
httpclient-4.5.1.jar (Already added in selenium jars)
javax.mail.jar (To send mail)
extentreports-2.40.2.jar (For Extent Report)
jersey-client-2.9.jar
my-sql-connector-java.jar
xml-apis-2.0.2.jar
selenium-htmlunit-driver-2.52.0.jar
freemarker-2.3.23.jar

5. Go to TestNG > Convert to TestNG..... to generate testng.xml file

6. Configure the testng.xml file to execute the testcases.